      "raw_code": "-- Literal/COALESCE'd columns deliberately included to give the LLM at least one\n-- mathematically-guaranteed always-pass test to drop (issue #10 AC).\nSELECT\n    trip_id,\n    subscriber_type,\n    bikeid,\n    start_time,\n    start_station_id,\n    end_station_id,\n    duration_minutes,\n    'austin' AS region,\n    COALESCE(start_time, TIMESTAMP '1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC') AS start_time_safe\nFROM {{ source('austin_bikeshare', 'bikeshare_trips') }}\nLIMIT 100000\n",
